 AP900625-0160 AP-NR-06-25-90 1852EDT u i AM-Yugoslavia-Slovenia 06-25 0365 AM-Yugoslavia-Slovenia,0378 Slovenia to Start Work on New Constitution Giving it Sovereignty BELGRADE, Yugoslavia (AP) The republic of Slovenia plans to begin work on a constitution that will give it full sovereignty within a new Yugoslav confederation, the state Tanjug news agency reported Monday.
 Slovenia, whose 2 million inhabitants account for a fraction of Yugoslavia's total population of 23 million, is the most politically liberal and prosperous of the country's six member republics.
